  "page": "House of the Dragon - Season 3",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:#f8e9d0;border:none;\"><i>House of the Dragon</i></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\nSeason 3</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">Country of origin</span></th><td>\nUnited States</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Network</th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HBO\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:HBO\">HBO</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#f8e9d0;border:none;\">Release</th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#f8e9d0;border:none;\">Season chronology</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<div style=\"display:inline-block;width:50%;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">←&#160;Previous</span><br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon_-_Season_2\" title=\"House of the Dragon - Season 2\">Season 2</a>\n            </div><div style=\"display:inline-block;width:50%;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Next&#160;→</span><br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon_-_Season_4\" title=\"House of the Dragon - Season 4\">Season 4</a></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;border:none;\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/List_of_House_of_the_Dragon_episodes\" title=\"List of House of the Dragon episodes\">List of episodes</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Season 3</b> of <i><a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"House of the Dragon\">House of the Dragon</a></i> is the third season of the series.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Pre-production\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Pre-production</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Cast\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Cast</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Pre-production\">Pre-production</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_of_the_Dragon_-_Season_3&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Pre-production\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><i>House of the Dragon</i> was officially renewed for a third season on the 13th June 2024, three days before the release of the first episode of the <a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon_-_Season_2\" title=\"House of the Dragon - Season 2\">second season</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The day after of the <a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon_-_Season_2\" title=\"House of the Dragon - Season 2\">season 2</a> finale aired, showrunner <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ryan_Condal\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Ryan Condal\">Ryan Condal</a> revealed season 3 is scheduled to enter production in early 2025. The scripts being currently worked on, the pre-production is planned for the fall 2024.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Cast\">Cast</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_of_the_Dragon_-_Season_3&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Cast\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">Main article: <a href=\"/index.php/List_of_actors_of_House_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"List of actors of House of the Dragon\">List of actors of House of the Dragon</a></div>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">See also: <a href=\"/index.php/List_of_characters_created_for_House_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"List of characters created for House of the Dragon\">List of characters created for House of the Dragon</a></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_of_the_Dragon_-_Season_3&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Variety: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://variety.com/2024/tv/news/house-of-the-dragon-renewed-season-3-1236036527/\">House of the Dragon Renewed for Season 3</a> (June 13, 2024)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Variety: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://variety.com/2024/tv/news/house-of-the-dragon-end-season-4-1236095543/\">\"House of the Dragon\" to End With Season 4, Season 3 to Begin Production in Early 2025</a> (August 5, 2024)</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_of_the_Dragon_-_Season_3&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: External links\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://gameofthrones.fandom.com/wiki/House_of_the_Dragon:_Season_3\">House of the Dragon: Season 3</a> on the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://gameofthrones.fandom.com/wiki/Wiki_of_Westeros\">Wiki of Westeros</a></li></ul>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:HOTD\" title=\"Template:HOTD\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:HOTD&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:HOTD (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:HOTD&amp;action=edit\"><span titl